<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Book Notes | Lin</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css">
</head>

<body>

    <header class="header">
        <div class="logo">Book Notes</div>

        <nav class="nav">
            <a href="/?sort=newest">Newest</a>
            <a href="/?sort=rating">Rating</a>

            <div class="dropdown">
                <button class="dropbtn">Genre ▾</button>
                <div class="dropdown-content">
                    <a href="/?genre=Fiction">Fiction</a>
                    <a href="/?genre=Thriller">Thriller / Horror</a>
                    <a href="/?genre=Self-Help">Self-Help</a>
                    <a href="/?genre=Philosophy">Philosophy / Spiritual</a>
                    <a href="/?genre=Autobiography">Autobiography</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a href="/?sort=title">Title (A→Z)</a>
        </nav>
    </header>


    <main class="container">

        <section class="intro">
            <h1>Books I’ve read</h1>
            <p>
                Welcome to my Book Notes! </br>Here, I keep track of all the books I’ve read, along with my personal
                ratings.
                I use this page to remember what I liked (or didn’t) and to share my opinions with anyone curious enough
                to look.
                I’ve uploaded a total of <%= totalBooks %> books.
                You’ll find a variety of genres, and the ratings reflect my own opinions. </br>

                If you’d like to discuss books, I’d be happy to hear from you! You can reach me via
                <a href="mailto:lynnlae22@gmail.com">email.</a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="book-grid">
            <% books.forEach(book=> { %>
                <a href="/book/<%= book.id %>" class="card-link">
                    <div class="book-card">
                        <img src="https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/<%= book.identifier_type %>/<%= book.identifier_value %>-M.jpg"
                            alt="Book cover" class="book-cover">

                        <h3 class="book-title">
                            <%= book.title %>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="book-author">
                            <%= book.author %>
                        </p>
                        <p class="book-genre">
                            <%= book.genre %>
                        </p>

                        <div class="details">
                            <span class="rating">Rating: <%= book.rating %>/10</span>
                            <span class="date">Added: <%= book.date_added %></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <% }) %>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>© <span id="year"></span> Book Notes. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Book cover images from Open Library and other online resources.</p>
        <!-- <p>Last updated: <%= books[0].date_added %> -->
        </p>
        <p>All opinions expressed are personal and do not reflect those of authors or publishers.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    </script>

</body>

</html>